{"tid":1066400,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"美斯贏咗今屆歐聯，無需去英超證明自己，原因如下","createTime":"2019-03-18T01:22:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-20T20:32:13.000Z","uid":43785,"like":74,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"1844c21277490a04ded592b2dc04541dd753b599","tid":1066400,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T01:22:00.000Z","msg":"有班人成日話你知，美斯要去英超踢波證明自己， 貶低西甲係次一級聯賽 。 計我話如果未試今屆贏咗歐聯根本就唔需要去英超證明自己，因為歐聯剩下對手已經全部都係英超球隊。 有足夠說服力，說明畀大家聽美斯有能力征服英超。 唔會踢英超踢斷腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n因為今屆美斯登基之路，賽程按正路對手就係咁既，<br />\n先斬曼聯，後殺利物浦，再踢贏曼城。<br />\n佢地分別係今屆英超第一名，第二名，及第四名。<br />\n<br />\n連續贏三隊英超奪得歐聯， 根本就無需要美斯去英超證明自己。 離開咗西甲一樣可以踢贏英超BIG4<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ca7400f69744f4ea61b0a671d9c1f86dd3c22a4","tid":1066400,"uid":25831,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T01:23:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2814554ca3c789adb4d2e433d9266907c6685808","tid":1066400,"uid":41434,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T01:24:42.000Z","msg":"咁邊隊英超第一"},{"pid":"90b224cfa3c9a285a06c15bfd0200f6dd3883e82","tid":1066400,"uid":10670,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T01:25:19.000Z","msg":"對埋狼隊先算"},{"pid":"26a31d51cd81c72d98eb05cccb8ad4bd7cb31c84","tid":1066400,"uid":43785,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"6ca7400f69744f4ea61b0a671d9c1f86dd3c22a4","tid":1066400,"uid":25831,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T01:23:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T01:25:54.000Z","msg":"c朗咪啞晒？都冇計。<br />\n按正路賽程，美斯就係要贏三隊英超封王<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\